user_name: HCT Community & School Aged Immunisation Service
text: Calling all 16 & 17 year olds come down to Hemel Hospital vaccination centre from 9  - 3.30 for a walk-in Covid jab! No queues! #CovidVaccine

We are pleased to share this weeks walk in clinics! Waiting times have been reduced and most patients can be in and out fairly quickly.
Come and see our friendly team!. Over 16s are now welcome to attend our walk in clinics.😃
#Covidvaccine #NHS #pfizervacine #AstraZeneca https://t.co/obljNFpX3Y
